data.description: Welcome to your dream home in Burton, Michigan! This charming 3-bedroom, 1.5-bath residence is the epitome of move-in readiness, boasting beautiful hardwood floors that add warmth and character to each room. Indulge in relaxation in the jetted tub, and experience the convenience of stainless steel appliances in the well-appointed kitchen. What sets this home apart is the added peace of mind provided by a whole-home generator, ensuring uninterrupted comfort in any situation. The bedrooms are generously sized, offering ample space and excellent storage solutions to accommodate your lifestyle seamlessly. The layout of this home is designed for both functionality and enjoyment, featuring a delightful living room as well as a bonus family room at the rear of the property. Access to the outdoors is made easy through a sliding glass door, allowing you to step onto a covered porch – the perfect spot to unwind and savor the evenings. The expansive yard is a haven for entertaining, providing ample space for gatherings and making lasting memories. Don't let this incredible opportunity slip away. Seize the chance to make this Burton gem your own and embrace a lifestyle of comfort, style, and endless enjoyment. Schedule your showing today and envision the possibilities that await.
